Functions:</span></h5><p class="Standard"><span class="T11">1) Search for a artist</span></p><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE FUNCTION searchartist (name varchar(50))  RETURNS int(11)</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">declare id int;</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">set id = (select artistid from artist where artistname = name);</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">if (id &gt; 0) then</span></p><p class="P75"><span class="T18">return id;</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">end if;</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">RETURN -1;</span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="P14"/><p class="Standard"><span class="T11">2) Search for a album</span></p><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE FUNCTION searchalbum (name varchar(50))  RETURNS int(11)</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">declare id int;</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">set id = (select albumid from artist where albumname = name);</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">if (id &gt; 0) then</span></p><p class="P75"><span class="T18">return id;</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">end if;</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">RETURN -1;</span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="Standard"> </p><p class="Standard"> </p><p class="Standard"> </p><p class="Standard"> </p><p class="Standard"> </p><p class="Standard"> </p><p class="Standard"> </p><p class="Standard"> </p><p class="Standard"> </p><p class="Standard"> </p><h5 class="Heading_20_5"><a id="a__6__Procedures_"><span/></a><span class="T10">6. Procedures:</span></h5><ol><li><p class="P51" style="margin-left:1.27cm;"><span style="display:block;float:left;min-width:0.635cm;">1)</span><span class="T11">Adding a Directory</span><span class="odfLiEnd"/> </p></li></ol><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE PROCEDURE adddirectory (in location varchar(500))</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">insert into directories values (location); </span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="P39"> </p><ol><li><p class="P51" style="margin-left:1.27cm;"><span style="display:block;float:left;min-width:0.635cm;">2)</span><span class="T11">Adding a Track</span><span class="odfLiEnd"/> </p></li></ol><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE PROCEDURE addtrack(in trackname varchar(50),in artistname varchar(50),in albumname varchar(100),in location varchar(500),in genre varchar(30))</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">Begin</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">declare artistid int; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">declare albumid int;</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">declare trackid int;</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">set trackid = (select newid from id);</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">set artistid = searchartist(artistname);</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">set albumid = searchalbum(albumname); </span></p><p class="P74"/><p class="P73"><span class="T18">insert into track(trackid,trackname,location,genre) values(trackid, trackname, location, genre);</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18"> if (artistid = -1) then</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">         set artistid = (select newid from id);</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">         insert into artist values (artistid, artistname); </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">end if; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">if (albumid = -1) then</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">         set albumid = (select newid from id); </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">        insert into album values (albumid, albumname);</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18"> end if; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">insert into trackinfo values (trackid, artistid, albumid);</span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18"> end</span></p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P29"><span class="T11">3) Adding a Track to a Playlist</span></p><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE PROCEDURE addtracktoplaylist (in pid int,in tid int)</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">declare torder int; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">set torder = (select count(*) from playlistinfo where playlistid=pid); </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">set torder = torder + 1; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">insert into playlistinfo values(pid,tid,torder); </span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="Standard"><span class="T12"> </span></p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P29"><span class="T11">4) Creating a PlayList</span></p><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE PROCEDURE createplaylist (in PlaylistName varchar(100))</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">declare pid int; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">set pid = (select playlistid from id); </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">insert into playlist values(pid,PlaylistName); </span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="P30"> </p><p class="P29"><span class="T11">5) Deleting a Directory</span></p><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE PROCEDURE deletedirectory (in location varchar(500))</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN         </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">declare tid int;  </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">declare trackids cursor for select trackid from track where track.location like concat(location, '%');     delete from directories where folderlocation = location;</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">     open trackids;</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">     get_trackid : LOOP         </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">        fetch trackids into tid;         </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">        call deletetrack(tid); </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">        end loop get_trackid;</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">       close trackids; </span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P29"><span class="T11">6) Deleting a track from a playlist</span></p><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE PROCEDURE deletefromplaylist (in pid int,in tid int)</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">declare torder int; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">set torder=(select trackorder from playlistinfo where playlistid=pid and trackid=tid);</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">delete from playlistinfo where playlistid=pid and trackid=tid; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">update playlistinfo set trackorder=trackorder-1 where playlistid=pid and trackorder&gt;torder; </span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P29"><span class="T11">7) Deleting a playlist</span></p><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE PROCEDURE deleteplaylist (in pid int)</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">delete from playlist where playlistid=pid;</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">delete from playlistinfo where playlistid=pid; </span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P29"><span class="T11">8) Deleting a track</span></p><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE PROCEDURE deletetrack (in TrackId int)</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">delete from track where track.trackid=TrackId; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">delete from trackinfo where trackinfo.trackid=TrackId; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">delete from playlistinfo where playlistinfo.trackid=TrackId; </span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P29"><span class="T11">9) Adding a track to Favourites</span></p><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE PROCEDURE favourite (in TrackId int)</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">update track set favourite=True where track.trackid=TrackId; </span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P29"><span class="T11">10) Moving a track in playlist (up or down)</span></p><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE PROCEDURE movetrack (in pid int, in tid int, in direction int)</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">declare swaptid int; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">declare torder int; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">set torder = (select trackorder from playlistinfo where playlistid = pid and trackid = tid); </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">if(direction = 0) then</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">     set swaptid = (select trackid from playlistinfo where playlistid = pid and trackorder = torder - 1);</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">     update playlistinfo set trackorder = torder where playlistid = pid and trackid = swaptid;</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">     update playlistinfo set trackorder = torder - 1 where playlistid = pid and trackid = tid; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">else </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">      set swaptid = (select trackid from playlistinfo where playlistid = pid and trackorder = torder + 1);</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">     update playlistinfo set trackorder = torder where playlistid = pid and trackid = swaptid;</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">     update playlistinfo set trackorder = torder + 1 where playlistid = pid and trackid = tid; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">end if; </span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P29"><span class="T11">11) Removing a track from Favourites</span></p><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE PROCEDURE unfavourite (in TrackId int)</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">update track set favourite=false where track.trackid=TrackId; </span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="P30"> </p><p class="P30"> </p><p class="P29"><span class="T11">12) Update a playlist name</span></p><p class="P76_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE PROCEDURE updateplaylist (in pid int, in newname varchar(50))</span></p><p class="P76"><span class="T18">BEGIN </span></p><p class="P76"><span class="T18">update playlist set playlistname = newname where playlistid = pid; </span></p><p class="P76_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P30"> </p><p class="P29"><span class="T11">13) Updating a track information</span></p><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE PROCEDURE updatetrack (in TrackId int,in newtrack varchar(50),in newartist varchar(50),in newalbum varchar(100),in newgenre varchar(30))</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">declare ArtistId int; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">declare AlbumId int; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">update track set trackname = newtrack, genre = newgenre where track.trackid = TrackId; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">set ArtistId=searchartist(newartist); </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">set AlbumId=searchalbum(newalbum); </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">if (ArtistId = -1) then</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">         set ArtistId=(select newid from id); </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">        insert into artist values (ArtistId,newartist); </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">end if; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">if (AlbumId = -1) then</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">         set AlbumId = (select newid from id);</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">         insert into album values (AlbumId,newalbum); </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">end if; </span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">update trackinfo set artistid=ArtistId, albumid=AlbumId where trackinfo.trackid = TrackId; </span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="Standard"> </p><p class="Standard"> </p><h5 class="Heading_20_5"><a id="a__7__Triggers_"><span/></a><span class="T10">7. Triggers:</span></h5><p class="P29"><span class="T11">1) Refresh artist and album after delete in trackinfo</span></p><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE TRIGGER deleterefresh AFTER DELETE ON trackinfo</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">FOR EACH ROW</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">DELETE FROM album WHERE albumid NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT albumid FROM trackinfo);</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">DELETE FROM artist WHERE artistid NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT artistid FROM trackinfo);</span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="P14"> </p><p class="P29"><span class="T11">2) Refresh artist and album after update in trackinfo</span></p><p class="P73_borderStart"><span class="T18">CREATE TRIGGER deleterefresh AFTER UPDATE ON trackinfo</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">FOR EACH ROW</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">BEGIN</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">DELETE FROM album WHERE albumid NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT albumid FROM trackinfo);</span></p><p class="P73"><span class="T18">DELETE FROM artist WHERE artistid NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT artistid FROM trackinfo);</span></p><p class="P73_borderEnd"><span class="T18">END</span></p><p class="P14"> </p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="P15"> </p><p class="Standard"> </p><h5 class="Heading_20_5"><a id="a__8__ER-DIAGRAM_OF_MUSIC_MANAGEMENT_SYSTEM"><span/></a><span class="T10">8. </span><span class="T20">ER-DIAGRAM OF MUSIC MANAGEMENT SYSTEM</span></h5><p class="P16"> </p><p class="P14"> </p><!--Next 'div' was a 'text:p'.--><div class="P10"><a id="_GoBack"/><!--Next '
